description: Hopes fade of finding more survivors from a powerful earthquake that hit eastern Turkey on Friday.
title: Turkey earthquake: Rescue efforts near end as death toll rises
title_page: Turkey earthquake: Rescue efforts near end as death toll rises - BBC News
maintext: Rescue teams worked through the night on Friday and Saturday in freezing temperatures, using their hands, drills and diggers to try to find people in the rubble of fallen buildings. They also brought beds and tents for those displaced.
